snippet.title: Official Trailer | 12 Labours of Hercules VI - Race for Olympus
snippet.description:
12 Labours of Hercules VI - Race for Olympus is now available in all app stores! Tag along on a breathtaking search for the kidnapped Zeus and visit exciting places you've never seen before.
Clear roads, construct buildings, battle beasts and more as you complete 50 challenging time management levels. Can you unravel who's behind Zeus's abduction? ▶︎▶︎▶︎ http://m.onelink.me/f7c3b389
